metadata.description: TateDAO, We are Distrupting the creator economy, Forget Instagram, Forget Facebook, Forget Harvard University — welcome to Hustler’s University: “a community” where students “learn Stocks, Crypto, E-commerce, Copywriting, and more”, where “a number of War Room members will teach YOU exactly how to make money online”, The P stands for Pimpin and the H stands for Hoes so D, Do the right thing and mint this shit! TateDAO is for the people, by the people. Own it, join our war room and lets cook. What color is YOUR bugatti?
